Project 2

REPORT
This project took about 12 hours to complete using python3. The code is seperated 
into two files, "cryptography.py" contains all of the cryptography algorithms. 
Caesor, Monoalphabetic and polyalphabetic were implemented with OOP and TTH is a function. 
"program.py" calls the algorithms and handle errors.

RUN
To run the program simply type "python program.py" in a terminal.
When prompted to enter a file name, ensure that the file or dictory containing the 
file is in the same directory as "program.py".
